id: 2720
name: "6130 Dictatorship A"
power: 2.0
text: |
  ais523 CAN cause this rule to amend itself with support from
  Janet.  Janet CAN cause this rule to amend itself with support
  from ais523.

  ais523 and Janet CAN each by announcement cause this rule to
  repeal a rule (other than this one) that was created during April
  2026 or May 2026 (but must, when doing so, specify which rule is
  being repealed).
